**Key Objectives of the Science and Technology Laws Amendment Bill:**

* Ensure that the same governance principles and operational procedures are applied across the public entities that report to the Department of Science and Innovation.
* Negate the inconsistent, inadequate and uncoordinated management of these entities, each of which have their own principle acts.
* Standardise governance and operational procedures of the public entities that report to the department allows the department to efficiently manage its administrative relationship with entities as well as more effective and strategic oversight of the entity boards and council.

