* The Science and Technology Laws Amendment Act 16 of 2011
* The Science and Technology Laws Amendment Act 7 of 2014

The current Science and Technology Laws Amendment Bill specifically focus on the following five principal acts which are:

* The 2001 Academy of Science of South Africa Act;
* The 2008 Human Science Research Act;
* The Science Research Council Act of 2008;
* The South African National Space Agency Act; and
* The Technology Innovation Act.

